{"version":1,"entries":{"person_2566616_translations":{"at":1774376983318,"data":{"id":2566616,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"At the age of 21, Honorine Magnier joined the Cochet course. She stayed there for two years. During this period, she had her first theatrical experiences, notably in Le Malade imaginaire , directed by René Camoin where she played Angélique . She will then spend a year at the Sudden workshops. While she has just passed the competition for the Studio-théâtre d'Asnières , Honorine Magnier prefers to accept the role of Valentine in the play Lady Oscar alongside Amanda Lear , and begins a long tour. She then goes on to perform roles intelevision series , such as My Worst Anguish or Les Petits Meurtres by Agatha Christie and in short films. After a new stint in the theater in the play Nelson , where she crosses paths with Chantal Ladesou and Armelle , Honorine Magnier was chosen in 2017 to play Rose Orsini in the TF1 series, Research Section. After having played in 28 episodes, she left the series in 2021 and then joined the cast of Tomorrow belongs to us on the same channel.","name":"Honorine Magnier","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CA","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"","name":"Honorine Magnier","primary":true}}]}},"person_1922640_translations":{"at":1774376997396,"data":{"id":1922640,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Shun Horie (堀江 瞬, Horie Shun, May 25, 1993) is a Japanese voice actor born in Osaka. He won the Best New Actor Award at the 12th Seiyu Awards. He is affiliated with Raccoon Dog and member of SparQlew. Previously, he was affiliated with Pro-Fit until March 2022.","name":"Shun Horie","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"호리에 슌","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"ES","iso_639_1":"es","name":"Español","english_name":"Spanish","data":{"biography":"Shun Horie (堀江 瞬, Horie Shun, 25 de mayo de 1993) es un actor de voz (seiyuu) japonés nacido en la prefectura de Osaka. Ganó el premio al Mejor Actor Revelación en los 12.º Seiyu Awards. Está afiliado a Raccoon Dog y es miembro de SparQlew. Anteriormente, estuvo afiliado a Pro-Fit hasta marzo de 2022.","name":"Shun Horie","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"堀江瞬是日本的男性聲優。出身於大阪府，所屬公司為 Raccoon Dog。","name":"堀江瞬","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"堀江瞬（ほりえ しゅん，Horie Shun），日本的男性声优，大阪府出生，事务所为Raccoon Dog。代表作品有《偶像活动stars!》香澄朝阳、《12岁。～小小胸口的怦然心动～》桧山一翔、《猜谜王》越山识、《偶像大师 SideM》皮埃尔、《十二大战》寝住、《皿三昧》阵内燕太、《租借女友》木之下和也、《我心里危险的东西》市川京太郎、《宝可梦地平线》艾梅吉欧、《原神》空等。","name":"堀江瞬","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"堀江瞬","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"Shun Horie","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TH","iso_639_1":"th","name":"ภาษาไทย","english_name":"Thai","data":{"biography":"","name":"ชุง โฮริเอะ","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CZ","iso_639_1":"cs","name":"Český","english_name":"Czech","data":{"biography":"","name":"Šun Horie","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"BR","iso_639_1":"pt","name":"Português","english_name":"Portuguese","data":{"biography":"","name":"Shun Horie","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Шюн Хоріе","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"堀江瞬是日本的男性聲優。出身於大阪府。隸屬於 Raccoon Dog。","name":"堀江瞬","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IT","iso_639_1":"it","name":"Italiano","english_name":"Italian","data":{"biography":"Shun Horie (堀江 瞬, Horie Shun) è un doppiatore giapponese nato il 25 maggio 1993 a Osaka. Ha vinto il premio come miglior nuovo attore alla dodicesima edizione dei Seiyu Awards. È affiliato a Raccoon Dog e membro di SparQlew. In precedenza, è stato affiliato a Pro-Fit fino al marzo 2022.","name":"Shun Horie","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Сюн Хориэ","primary":false}}]}},"person_1579819_translations":{"at":1774377003818,"data":{"id":1579819,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"대한민국의 배우.\n\n연극과 영화를 오가면서 필모그래피를 쌓다가 드라마 '슬기로운 의사생활'의 허선빈 역, 이후 드라마 '이상한 변호사 우영우'의 최수연 역을 연기하면서 이름을 알리기 시작했다.\n\n과거 고등학교 2학년 때 입시 준비를 하면서부터 연기를 시작했다고 한다. 평소 체육과 미술 등 예체능 계열을 좋아했지만 진로 고민을 하던 중 영화와 공연을 많이 보러 다녔던 자신이 연기에 관심이 있다는 것을 알게 되면서 연극을 해보고 싶어서 부모님을 설득하였지만 반대했다고 한다.\n\n본가가 일산이고 부모님은 일부러 고생하면 포기할 것이라 생각하여 서울에 있는 학원까지 보냈지만 생각보다 너무 잘하고 있어서 놀랐고 학원 시험에서도 좋은 성적을 얻어 오히려 본인의 꿈을 지지해주기 시작했다고 한다.\n\n이후 2015년 연극으로 데뷔하였고, 이후에는 영화 '소셜포비아' 에서 처음으로 주연을 맡으며 상업영화에 출연하였으며, 독립영화 쪽에서 활발하게 연기 활동을 하였다.","name":"하윤경","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"河允京 ： 1992 年 10 月 20 日（29 岁)，韩国，身高： 1.65 米 43kg, O型血\n\n教育背景： 韩国艺术综合大学  首次亮相  2015 年播放“罗克珊的歌谣”","name":"河允京","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Ha Yoon-kyung (born October 20, 1992) is a South Korean actress. She is best known for her roles in television series such as Hospital Playlist (2020–2021), Extraordinary Attorney Woo (2022), and See You in My 19th Life (2023).","name":"Ha Yoon-kyung","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"MX","iso_639_1":"es","name":"Español","english_name":"Spanish","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"河允景（하윤경，Ha Yoon-kyung）或譯河潤景，韓國女演員。","name":"河允景","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Ха Юн Гён","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"河允景 ： 1992 年 10 月 20 日（29 歲)，韓國，身高： 1.65 米 43kg, O 型血\n\n教育背景： 韓國藝術綜合大學 首次亮相 2015 年播放“羅克珊的歌謠”","name":"河允景","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Ха Юн Кьон","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"","name":"Ha Yoon-kyung","primary":false}}]}},"tv_256783_keywords":{"at":1774377005054,"data":{"id":256783,"results":[{"name":"based on novel or book","id":818},{"name":"courtesan","id":4178},{"name":"romance","id":9840},{"name":"transmigration","id":12320},{"name":"donghua","id":315535}]}},"person_1475555_translations":{"at":1774377007254,"data":{"id":1475555,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"BR","iso_639_1":"pt","name":"Português","english_name":"Portuguese","data":{"biography":"Gabriel Leone Coutinho Miranda Frota é um ator brasileiro.\n\nGabriel começou a carreira com 16 anos enquanto estava no colégio, entrou numa peça de teatro onde foi convocado a entrar na companhia de teatro \"Cia. Teatral Notre Dame\" do diretor da peça, permaneceu na cia de 2009 até 2013, atuando nesses anos em seis peças da Cia como A Megera Domada, Bailei na Curva e A Vida é Sonho. Em seguida, atuou em espetáculos musicais, como Rapsódia de Liane Maya e viveu o rei Roberto Carlos em Chacrinha de Andrucha Waddington.\n\nEm 2013, estreia na televisão numa participação na série A Grande Família e em seguida na Malhação, mas foi em Verdades Secretas que ficou conhecido pelo público no papel de Gui, um jovem rico sustentado pelos pais. Em 2016 viveu seu primeiro protagonista no horário nobre, Miguel de Sá Ribeiro em Velho Chico, o filho de Tereza, papel de Camila Pitanga. Em 2017, entra pra supersérie Os Dias Eram Assim, vivendo o revolucionário Gustavo Reis. Em outubro de 2018, começa a rodar o filme Meu Álbum de Amores, uma comédia romântica musical de Rafael Gomes, no papel principal do dentista Júlio.","name":"Gabriel Leone","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Gabriel Leone Coutinho Miranda Frota (Rio de Janeiro, July 21, 1993) is Brazilian actor who has worked in television and film.","name":"Gabriel Leone","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"加布里埃尔·莱昂内（1993年7月21日，里约热内卢）是巴西演员，曾在电视和电影领域工作。","name":"加布里埃尔·莱昂内","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TH","iso_639_1":"th","name":"ภาษาไทย","english_name":"Thai","data":{"biography":"","name":"กาเบรียล ลิโอน","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Габриэль Леоне","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"加布里埃爾·莱昂","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"加布裏埃爾·萊昂（1993 年 7 月 21 日，裏約熱內盧）是巴西演員，曾在電視和電影領域工作。","name":"加布裏埃爾·萊昂","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Ґебріел Леоне","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"ガブリエル・レオン","primary":false}}]}},"person_2304087_translations":{"at":1774377016850,"data":{"id":2304087,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Ali Fikry (born March 7, 2008) is an Indonesian actor.","name":"Ali Fikry","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"ID","iso_639_1":"id","name":"Bahasa indonesia